/ *
     ATTENTION RUBY MUST BE INSTALLED !!
     IN CONCLUSION MUST be executed 'gem install sass'.
     Possibly. the PC must be restarted several times.
* /


/ * Only JS + CSS * /
1. Terminal: npm link or npm install
2. Right-click gulpfile.js: Run 'default'


/ * Patternlab + JS / CSS * /
1. Terminal: composer install
     -> n in the query to change the config
2. npm link

3. Right-click on the Gulp-file run 'default'

4. Run / Edit Configuration / PHP Scripts
4.1. + (create new PHP script)
4.2. Name Patternlab
4.3. Select file: <PATH> / styleguide / core / console
4.4. Arguments: --watch
4.5. Start the 'Patternlab' process